<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><br />
<strong>SCP-CN-1364</strong>-欲加之惧</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5480202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="sciencekiller" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5480202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;">sciencekiller</a></span>和<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3290685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609247507" alt="Rye Travis" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3290685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;">Rye Travis</a></span></p>
